cu.explanation_en: Setting the PHY log level to an unknown value will cause PHY layer logging to fail, potentially obscuring PHY-related issues and hindering low-level debugging.

du.explanation_en: Setting the PHY log level to an unknown value will cause PHY layer logging to fail, potentially obscuring PHY-related issues and hindering low-level debugging.
du.explanation_zh: 將 PHY 日誌級別設定為未知值會導致 PHY 層日誌失敗，可能遮蔽 PHY 相關問題並阻礙低級除錯。
